org.eclipse.keyple.calypso.command.po.parser

Class SelectFileRespPars

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.keyple.core.command.AbstractApduResponseParser
      • org.eclipse.keyple.calypso.command.po.AbstractPoResponseParser
        • org.eclipse.keyple.calypso.command.po.parser.SelectFileRespPars

  • public final class SelectFileRespPars
extends AbstractPoResponseParser
    This class provides status code properties and the getters to access to the structured fields of data from response to a Select File command (available from the parent class).

    The FCI structure is analyzed and all subfields are made available through as many getters.
